@node intro "Introduction.."

  @{fg shine}@{b}Intro
  ~~~~~@{ub}@{fg text}

   This is a tetris clone based on MUI.

   It has a lot of features like:

   * Freely configurable playfield size between 6x10 blocks to 30x40 blocks
   * 5 levels of difficulty
   * 18 new larger 5-block pieces
   * 4 new smaller 3-, 2- and 1-block pieces
   * Optional random lines at start, 1 to 20 random lines
   * 2-player game locally or over Internet
   * Fully configurable keys for game control
   * Editable colours for every piece using pens, or RGB for GFX-card users
   * An infinite number of games can be saved
   * Inverse logarithmic level increment
   * And much more..!


@endnode

@node req "Requirements.."

  @{fg shine}@{b}Requirements
  ~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}@{fg text}

   OS version 37+

   MUI - Magical User Interface V3

   Preferably a graphics card to use RGB colours and
   get the most out of the game.


@endnode

