@node usage "Usage.."

  @{fg shine}@{b}Usage
  ~~~~~@{ub}@{fg text}

   This will explain the different settings in Detris so that you
   can get the most out of it.

   But first I will explain two different things; blocks and pieces.
   A block is a square of which pieces are buildt with.
   Pieces are the things in different shapes that falls down on
   the screen and that you are supposed to control and place right
   on the playfield.
   The standard tetris pieces consists of 4 blocks each.

