    the background or makes a flick!

  @{fg fill}*@{fg text} Now you can select if you want the outline to be drawn
    around the whole pieces instead of around every block as
    before!

  @{fg fill}*@{fg text} Now you can enable Esc key for quick quit and "p" is now
    used for pause/unpause and "n" for New game!

  @{fg fill}*@{fg text} I have removed alot of enforcer hits.


