@node reg "Registration.."

  @{fg shine}@{b}Registration
  ~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}@{fg text}

   Please use the internal "Easy register" that pops up
   when you start the program! You can also reach it from
   the Project menu.
   It's no online full-auto thing that might scare off some ppl..!

   Detris is Key-mail Ware which means that you have to
   send me an e-mail with your name to get a key-file so
   you can get rid of all annoying requesters! :-)
   It's absolutely free, I just want to see what program
